					"id": "ui_towing_desc",
					"value": {
						"text": "<bad>Your ship has been damaged and is incapacitated.</bad>\nPlease select a towing destination and pay the corresponding fee.\nOur towing service will be on its way to secure the remains of your ship as soon as possible.\n<bad>WARNING:</bad> We cannot be held liable for any additional damage or loss of cargo during the towing process."
					}
				},
