					"value": {
						"text": "The Shop only contains cosmetic items designed to make you look cooler, or whatever happens to be trendy across the Galaxy.\nThe Shop is NOT related to the greedy The Company, but by the (much more friendlier) \"The Devs\", a collective of artists and engineers dedicated to improving your overall happiness in this world.\nThe Devs are committed to ensuring that the Shop items will never provide any in-game advantages (unless you consider looking good an advantage, but that's up to you). This is a promise."
