				},
				{
					"id": "menu_choose_quadrant",
					"value": {
						"text": "Please select your *Quadrant*. A quadrant is a region of the galaxy inhabited by a community of explorers. Although you will be able to change quadrants later, it is generally best to start in the same quadrant as your friends, or in a different one from your enemies."
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "menu_confirm_quadrant",
					"value": {
						"text": "Confirm joining Quadrant *::id::*?"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "menu_player",
					"value": {
						"text": "[::level::] ::name::"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "demo",
					"value": {
						"group": [
							{
								"id": "end_title",
								"value": {
									"text": "Thank you for playing the *Demo!*"
								}
							},
							{
								"id": "end_subtitle",
								"value": {
									"text": "Early Access release Q2 2026"
								}
							},
							{
								"id": "start_title",
								"value": {
									"text": "Welcome to the SpaceCraft Demo!"
								}
							},
							{
								"id": "start_text",
								"value": {
									"text": "This version of the game is focused on introducing you to exploration, resource gathering, ship building, and helping us to collect your feedback.\n\nWhen SpaceCraft launches in *Early Access in Q2 2026*, you’ll be able to explore a vast galaxy filled with more diverse planets, rarer resources, and new challenges.\n\n*Base deployment and automation* will allow you to refine materials and scale production across multiple systems. *Interplanetary logistics* will let you connect your operations and manage large industrial networks.\n\nWe will also introduce *Corporations*, enabling you to create or join *player-driven organizations* and work together to complete large-scale missions, manage shared assets, and compete with other Corporations.\n\nWe hope you enjoy the demo. Wishlist SpaceCraft on Steam to stay up to date as we reveal more features!"
								}
							}
						]
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "cistern_tank",
					"value": {
						"text": "Tank"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "cistern_other",
					"value": {
						"text": "Base Cistern"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "popups_planet_discover_progress",
					"value": {
						"text": "DISCOVERY"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "permits_requires",
					"value": {
						"text": "Requires: <bad>::name::</bad>"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "permits_upkeep_price",
					"value": {
						"text": "Upkeep: <corpo-price>::value::</corpo-price>"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "unknown_object",
					"value": {
						"text": "&lt;???&gt;"
					}
				},
				{
					"id": "welcome_tests",
					"value": {
						"text": "Welcome to the SpaceCraft Playtest!\n\nWe're excited to have you on board and hope you will enjoy playing the current version of the game.\nThis playtest gives you access to an BETA version of SpaceCraft, so please keep the following points in mind when playing:\n\nWe are using this playtest to gather your feedback and improve the game. You may encounter bugs, disconnections, or data loss. Please report any issues or feedback using the REPORT button in the main menu. We will do our best to address any issues as quickly as possible.\n\nOptimization is still in progress. If you experience any performance issues, please report them using the REPORT button and include your hardware specs in your report.\n\nYour data and progression may be wiped during the playtest and nothing will carry over to the Early Access release.\n\nThe game is currently only available in English; more languages will be added later in development. You may notice typos or grammatical errors. These will be corrected later in development.\n\nThe server is EU-based and will not be online 24/7. More servers will be added later in development. If you're playing from outside the EU region, you may experience higher ping.\n\nNo NDA is required, so feel free to share screenshots, recordings, and gameplay online. If you are a content creator, please contact us at *community@shirogames.com*\n\nThis version is not yet suitable for full release. Additional content, such as combat, will be added to the playtest once it is ready to be tested. You can read more about upcoming content <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/3276050/SpaceCraft/\">*here*</a>.\n\nThank you for taking part in this playtest, and have fun playing SpaceCraft!\n\n- Shiro Games"
					}
				},
